    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/32f52fbc9414a8f0562581a3410dc7dc.avif?t=1726817834\" width=610 height=150 /></span> 。<br><br>通往Devadatta之路》是一款第一人称的冒险游戏，侧重于故事和解谜，以取得进展。<br>当你揭开围绕Devadatta的神秘面纱时，探索古老的遗迹!<br>用你的智慧逃离废墟，解决聪明的（有时是致命的）谜题，并避免被居住在废墟的生物杀死。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/650f7bbd7a34fbadcb8b3282e2db8a71.poster.avif?t=1726817834\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/650f7bbd7a34fbadcb8b3282e2db8a71.webm?t=1726817834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/650f7bbd7a34fbadcb8b3282e2db8a71.mp4?t=1726817834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 。<br><br>每个试验都会给你带来新的挑战，耐心或速度可能决定结果。<br><br>你会遇到各种复杂的谜题和物理谜题，你需要解决这些问题才能在故事中取得进展。<br><br><strong>你并不孤单</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"{STEAM_APP_IMAGE}/extras/Fire1.gif\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" /></span>[/img)<br><br>危险可能非常接近，你需要留意那个执意要追杀你的奇怪生物。<br>它是什么，它为什么要杀你？<br><br><strong>你并不孤单</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/cf053d884001019151836b026e34346b.avif?t=1726817834\" width=610 height=150 /></span><br><br><i>跟随Devadatta的脚步</i>。<br><br>阿罗是罗伯特的侄子，他的整个童年都和他在一起。他已经很久没有他的消息了，于是决定去找他。<br><br>阿洛将开始寻找答案，并在不知不觉中追随德瓦达塔的脚步，发现他叔叔失踪背后的可怕秘密。<br><br><strong>你不是 <br>你是 <br>孤独</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176880/extras/8d47ab832923c45934abef8ddf16dbb3.poster.avif?t=1726817834\" width=600 height=338 >